{{refimprove|date=January 2013}} [[File:Adam Hanuszkiewicz Polish actor 1966.jpg|200px|thumbnail|Adam Hanuszkiewicz]] '''Adam Hanuszkiewicz''' (16 June 1924 – 4 December 2011) was a [[Poles|Polish]] actor and theatre director.<ref>{{cite web|author=Am |url=http://kultura.newsweek.pl/adam-hanuszkiewicz-nie-zyje,85345,1,1.html |title=Adam Hanuszkiewicz nie żyje. Odszedł wybitny aktor i reżyser - Wiadomości - Newsweek.pl |publisher=Kultura.newsweek.pl |date=1970-01-01 |accessdate=2011-12-04}}</ref>
Hanuszkiewicz was born in [[Lwów]], [[Poland]]. He died in Warsaw, aged 87.
