'''Korea Computer Centre Sinhung Company''' is a [[software development]] group headquartered in [[Pyongyang]], [[North Korea]].  The company is involved in software on order, [[bioinformatics]], [[video games]], [[multimedia]] and [[recognition systems]].{{Citation needed|date=October 2012}}

It imports software, hardware, [[computer network|network]] equipment and other electronics into Korea.{{citation needed|date=October 2012}}

