istory of the Byzantine State and Society|author=Treadgold, W.T.|date=1997|publisher=Stanford University Press|isbn=978-0-8047-2630-6|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nYbnr5XVbzUC|page=702}}</ref><ref name="google199">{{cite book|title=The Balkans and the Near East: Introduction to a Shared History|author=Karl Kaser|date=2011|publisher=Lit|isbn=978-3-643-50190-5|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=j3i8muwLf8AC|page=196}}</ref><ref name="google200">{{cite book|title=Once Upon a Time|author=Barber, R.|date=2004|publisher=Sword of the Lord Publishers|isbn=978-0-87398-639-7|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=t-xCJGwPOZEC|page=335}}</ref><ref name="google201">{{cite book|title=The Wilton Translation of the New Testament|author=Wilton, C.C.|date=2012|publisher=Trafford Publishing|isbn=978-1-4669-0856-7|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JTtwQOrEyqsC|page=285}}</ref> |- |[[Trakai]] | | | | | | | | | | | | | |50,000 | | | | |<ref name="XiGLBQAAQBAJ 2060" /> |- |[[Veliko Tarnovo|Trnovo]] | | | | | | | | | | | |48,000 |35,000 | | | | | |<ref name="XiGLBQAAQBAJ 2060" /> |- |[[Târgoviște|Targoviste]] | | | | | | | | | | | | | |25,000-40,000 |50,000-60,000 |45,000-60,000 | | |<ref name="XiGLBQAAQBAJ 2060" /> |- |[[Trier]] | |70,000-80,000-100,000 |70,000-80,000-100,000 | | | | |15,000 | |20,000 | | | | | | | | |<ref name="isites.harvard.edu" /><ref name="google164" /><ref name="landesmuseum-trier">{{cite web|url=http://www.landesmuseum-trier.de/lib/02_Programm/antikencard-trier-englisch-2012.pdf|date=8 March 2012|title=AntiquitiesCard|publisher=TRIER THE CENTER OF ANTIQUITY IN GERMANY|accessdate=2014-09-24}}</ref><ref name="google202">{{cite book|title=Europe by Eurail 2010: Touring Europe by Train|author=LaVerne, F.K.|publisher=Globe Pequot Press|isbn=978-0-7627-6163-0|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ux7EOl11e34C|page=337|year=1991}}</ref><ref name="google203">{{cite book|title=Beyond Our World: The Exciting Story of a Treasure Hunter, Historian, and Adventur