[[Image:Sky Active.jpg|right]]
'''Sky Active''' is the brand name for [[Interactive television|interactive features]] on [[Sky Digital (UK & Ireland)|Sky Digital]] and is available in the UK and the [[Republic of Ireland]]. It enables a viewer to interact with TV content, respond to an advertisement or access internet-based services.

The service replaces [[Open....]] which helped launch Sky Digital's interactive content, and launched many other features that viewers see today such as games, emailing and [[shopping]] via their TV.

It can be accessed by pressing the [[Red Button (Digital Television)|red button]] on a Sky Digital [[Remote control (television)|remote]], while watching any Sky Digital Channel. Alternatively, there is an entry in the "Interactive" area of the [[Electronic program guide|EPG]].

